<!-- PROMPT GRID -->
<section class="py-5">
<div class="container">
<h2 class="mb-4 text-center">Best Professional Headshot Prompts</h2>
<div class="row g-4">
<!-- 1 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<img alt="professional ai headshot" class="img-fluid" loading="lazy" src="images/headshot/professional-ai-headshot.webp"/>
<h5>Corporate Studio Headshot</h5>
<small>Clean  Corporate</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p1">
                Create a professional corporate headshot from my photo. Place the subject in a premium photography
                studio with a neutral office-style background in soft grey or warm taupe. Use classic three-point studio
                lighting with a large softbox as key light, a fill reflector to soften shadows, and a subtle hair light
                for separation. The subject should be framed from the chest up with sharp focus on the eyes and face,
                preserving natural skin tones and texture without over-smoothing. The final image should look like a
                real DSLR photograph taken by a professional corporate photographer, suitable for company websites,
                email signatures, and business cards.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p1')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 2 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<img alt="linkedin headshot ai" class="img-fluid" loading="lazy" src="images/headshot/linkedin-headshot.webp"/>
<h5>LinkedIn Professional Photo</h5>
<small>Formal  Clean</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p2">
                Generate a clean LinkedIn profile picture with the subject wearing formal business attire  a
                well-tailored dark blazer over a light blue dress shirt with the top button open for an approachable yet
                professional look. The expression should be confident and warm, with a natural slight smile that conveys
                trustworthiness and competence. Soft, diffused studio lighting from a large umbrella creates even,
                flattering illumination across the face without harsh shadows. The background is a smooth, clean
                gradient from medium grey to lighter grey, creating a timeless corporate aesthetic. The image should be
                high-resolution and perfectly composed for the LinkedIn profile picture circle crop.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p2')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 3 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<img alt="office portrait ai" class="img-fluid" loading="lazy" src="images/headshot/office-portrait.webp"/>
<h5>Modern Office Portrait</h5>
<small>Professional  Natural</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p3">
                Create a professional office headshot with the subject positioned in a modern open-plan workspace. The
                background shows a tastefully blurred office environment with soft bokeh of computer monitors, indoor
                plants, and warm ambient lighting, creating depth and context without distraction. The subject is in
                sharp focus wearing business casual attire with balanced, natural-looking lighting that combines
                overhead office fluorescents with window light. Colors are realistic and true-to-life with neutral white
                balance. The composition frames the subject from mid-chest up, slightly off-center with the office
                environment providing professional context, ideal for team pages and company intranets.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p3')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 4 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<img alt="executive portrait ai" class="img-fluid" loading="lazy" src="images/headshot/executive.webp"/>
<h5>Executive CEO Style</h5>
<small>Premium  Formal</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p4">
                A corporate executive portrait featuring the subject in a dark tailored suit with a silk tie,
                photographed with dramatic studio lighting that creates bold shadows and highlights reminiscent of a
                premium business magazine cover shoot. A single key light from the upper left carves out the bone
                structure while a subtle fill prevents the shadows from going completely dark. The background is a deep,
                rich charcoal that fades to near-black. The image has a cinematic color grade with warm skin tones
                against cool shadows, creating a powerful sense of authority and success. Shot with a 85mm lens at f/2
                for beautiful subject isolation and gallery-quality sharpness.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p4')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 5 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<img alt="resume headshot ai" class="img-fluid" loading="lazy" src="images/headshot/resume-photo.webp"/>
<h5>Resume Profile Photo</h5>
<small>Simple  Formal</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p5">
                A professional resume headshot with the subject wearing crisp formal attire  a well-pressed white dress
                shirt beneath a classic navy blazer. The background is a clean, seamless white or very light grey with
                no gradients or textures, meeting standard resume photo requirements across industries. The subject
                maintains perfect formal posture with shoulders squared to the camera and chin slightly elevated for a
                confident, competent appearance. Soft studio lighting is perfectly balanced to illuminate both sides of
                the face evenly with no distracting shadows. The image is captured with razor-sharp facial clarity,
                clear enough to print at high resolution without any loss of detail.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p5')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 6 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<img alt="business casual headshot ai" class="img-fluid" loading="lazy" src="images/headshot/business-casual.webp"/>
<h5>Business Casual Headshot</h5>
<small>Friendly  Professional</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p6">
                A warm and inviting business casual profile picture featuring the subject in smart-casual attire  a
                fitted button-down shirt with rolled sleeves or a clean polo shirt in a muted, pleasant color. The
                subject displays a relaxed, genuine smile that conveys approachability and friendliness while
                maintaining professionalism. Soft, enveloping studio light from a large diffused source creates a
                bright, airy feel with minimal shadows and a fresh, modern aesthetic. The background is a clean, neutral
                tone that complements the outfit without competing for attention. The overall image feels contemporary
                and personable, perfect for startups, creative agencies, and customer-facing profiles.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p6')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 7 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<img alt="premium corporate portrait ai" class="img-fluid" loading="lazy" src="images/headshot/premium-corporate.webp"/>
<h5>Premium Corporate Portrait</h5>
<small>Luxury  Branding</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p7">
                A high-end corporate portrait that exudes premium quality and executive presence. The subject is posed
                with confident body language  arms subtly crossed or one hand on a lapel  wearing a bespoke suit with
                visible attention to tailoring details. The background features an out-of-focus luxury office
                environment with rich wood paneling, leather furniture, and warm accent lighting that speaks to success
                and achievement. Every detail in the image is rendered with crisp, magazine-quality clarity, from the
                texture of the suit fabric to the individual hairs of perfectly groomed brows. The color palette is rich
                and warm with deep browns, warm skin tones, and subtle golden highlights.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p7')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 8 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<img alt="minimal professional headshot ai" class="img-fluid" loading="lazy" src="images/headshot/minimal-headshot.webp"/>
<h5>Minimal Professional Headshot</h5>
<small>Modern  Clean</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p8">
                A minimal, modern headshot with a stripped-back aesthetic that puts all emphasis on the face. The
                subject is photographed against a simple, solid neutral background  pure white, light grey, or soft
                beige  with zero distractions or visual noise. Natural lighting from a large window provides soft,
                directional illumination that creates gentle modeling on the face with beautiful, organic shadows. The
                composition is a tight head-and-shoulders crop with the face occupying at least 60% of the frame. The
                image has a clean, contemporary feel with natural colors and no heavy post-processing, embodying the
                'less is more' philosophy of modern minimalist design.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p8')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 9 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<img alt="cinematic professional portrait ai" class="img-fluid" loading="lazy" src="images/headshot/cinematic-headshot.webp"/>
<h5>Cinematic Professional Portrait</h5>
<small>Polished  Dramatic</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p9">
                A professional cinematic headshot that elevates a standard corporate photo into an artistic statement.
                The shallow depth of field at f/1.4 creates a silky smooth background blur that makes the subject appear
                to float against an ethereal wash of muted colors. Subtle dramatic lighting uses a slightly lower key
                ratio than typical corporate photography, adding Rembrandt-style shadows that create depth and visual
                intrigue while remaining workplace-appropriate. The subject's expression is confident and compelling,
                photographed at a slight three-quarter angle for dynamic composition. The image receives a polished
                corporate finish with refined color grading  slightly lifted blacks, warm midtones, and crisp
                highlights  resulting in a headshot that is simultaneously professional and artistically distinctive.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p9')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
